      "acceptanceCriteria": "E/uval < 1.96 for all three QoIs; percent difference between mean FEA prediction and mean experimental result < 10%.",
      "rationale": "Stiffness: mean FEA 187 N/mm vs. mean experimental 182 N/mm (2.7% difference), E/uval = 0.84. Yield force: 4.3% difference, E/uval = 1.12. Force at 40 mm: 6.1% difference, E/uval = 1.47. All three QoIs satisfy both acceptance criteria. Comparison performed per ASME V&V 40 Section 5.3 validation metric methodology."
