    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for Medium model risk. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is acknowledged and accepted because ASTM F1717 defines a single standard test condition and no regulatory alternative exists. All three QoIs satisfy both quantitative acceptance criteria (percent difference <10%, E/uval <1.96). The FEA model ensemble is judged credible for the stated COU.",
